New -autoLogon command line option, usage sample:
  -autoLogon "5;Utente;Parola d'ordine;valentino;password"
where:
  "5" is the number of fields showed on the logon page
  "Utente" is the italian label for the user field (the one showed on the left of it) 
  "Parola d'ordine" is the italian label for the password field
  "valentino" is the user name
  "password" is its password

---  

New -hideMenuBar and -hideToolBar options, thanks to -hideMenuBar / -hideToolBar.     